# Rust core build artifacts
rust/target/

# Real backup archives carry a real passphrase + real borrower PII — NEVER
# commit them (AGENTS.md §2a / §12.7). The synthetic hermetic test vault under
# test/fixtures/vault/ (public throwaway passphrase, fake rows) IS committed.
*.pitabak
*.pitabak.*
android/build/

# M6: Android release signing material — NEVER commit. Only the .example
# template and the build wiring are tracked; the real secrets stay local.
android/key.properties
*.jks
*.keystore
